overview: The user wanted to significantly enhance the aesthetics of their sleep
  questionnaire app. The agent initiated a comprehensive review, identifying
  areas like the generic color palette, bland backgrounds, and basic form
  elements. The approach involved implementing a new, calming sleep-themed color
  palette with custom CSS variables and utility classes. The main questionnaire
  form layout was redesigned with decorative background elements and an improved
  progress indicator. The intro section was transformed with a hero component
  and feature cards. All core UI components, including checkboxes, radio
  buttons, sliders, and cards, were restyled for a more polished look.
  Crucially, all 14 individual questionnaire sections were systematically
  updated to use consistent, themed card-style groupings and text colors.
  Additionally, a console error related to  values being passed to input
  fields was diagnosed and fixed in the  component. The outcome is a
  cohesive, professional, and visually appealing application that effectively
  conveys a calming sleep health theme.
